00:14:51.615 --> 00:14:54.279
ker sem odrasla in
znam poskrbeti zase.

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:56.798
Sem videl maloprej.

00:14:56.998 --> 00:14:57.998
Ja.

00:14:58.039 --> 00:15:00.367
Kako je tvoja babica?

