00:15:20.320 --> 00:15:23.283
Videti si, kot da
bi prišel iz pekla.

00:15:23.483 --> 00:15:26.185
Videla sem plakate
s katerimi te iščejo.

00:15:26.185 --> 00:15:29.107
Še vedno bežiš
pred zakonom?

00:15:29.307 --> 00:15:31.592
Stranke imam.

00:15:31.592 --> 00:15:35.612
Če te kdo vpraša ali
me poznaš, reci da ne.

00:15:36.519 --> 00:15:39.154
To sploh ne bo težko.

00:15:47.159 --> 00:15:50.014
Nikoli si nisem mislila,
da te bom še kdaj videla.

00:15:57.440 --> 00:15:59.747
Pozdravljene, dame.

00:16:01.720 --> 00:16:03.210
Veseli me, da
sem te spoznal.

00:16:03.559 --> 00:16:04.890
Čudovita si.

00:16:06.639 --> 00:16:09.324
Lepo zahvaljeni, gospa.

00:16:10.279 --> 00:16:11.999
Dame.

00:16:17.279 --> 00:16:19.791
Čudovita si.

00:16:28.279 --> 00:16:29.725
Imam golo dekle ...

00:16:58.159 --> 00:17:02.682
Želim vedeti več o posebni
škatli iz kosti, mama.

00:17:02.882 --> 00:17:06.789
To ni palica, ki bi si jo
želel pobrati, sin.

00:17:06.789 --> 00:17:11.622
Ali veš kje je? -Nikoli
je ne bi smeli najti.

00:17:11.822 --> 00:17:13.993
Čigar last je,

00:17:15.493 --> 00:17:18.332
ta drži ključ do
neslutene oblasti nad zlom.

00:17:18.332 --> 00:17:21.674
Jackson jo želi imeti.
Grozil je meni

00:17:22.599 --> 00:17:24.963
in vsej moji družini.

00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:29.860
Vedno ti sledi tema,
Guerrero.

00:17:30.440 --> 00:17:33.242
Stara ženska sem, sinko.

00:17:33.442 --> 00:17:35.905
Ne bom več dolgo
na tem svetu,

00:17:37.319 --> 00:17:40.293
