si želiš biti.

00:18:42.173 --> 00:18:45.911
Ne moreš dovoliti, da bi
zmagal Jackson Boomer.

00:18:47.039 --> 00:18:49.751
Obljubi mi.
-Ne morem.

00:18:50.880 --> 00:18:55.050
