Kaj je narobe?

00:19:46.519 --> 00:19:49.537
Daj no. Nehaj že.

00:21:00.400 --> 00:21:02.836
Skušal si me ubiti.

00:21:02.836 --> 00:21:05.587
Pa ne tebe, ampak
samo tvojega konja.

00:21:05.787 --> 00:21:09.640
To je samo eden od mnogih načinov
s katerimi te bom prizadel,

00:21:09.720 --> 00:21:12.253
da bom dobil,
kar si želim.

00:21:12.253 --> 00:21:17.711
In želim si tisto škatlo,
Guerrero in to takoj.

00:21:18.211 --> 00:21:20.378
Pomirite se, fantje.

00:21:20.378 --> 00:21:23.575
Pomiri se, partner.
Pogovorimo se notri.

00:21:26.599 --> 00:21:29.039
Pojdite noter!
Pojdite noter!

00:21:29.239 --> 00:21:30.974
To ne bo mogoče.

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:34.385
Si prepričan,
da si želiš ta spopad?

00:21:34.385 --> 00:21:38.468
Prepričan sem, da si ga ne,
toda da bi dobil tisto knjigo,

00:21:38.968 --> 00:21:41.681
moram zabobnati
na bobne vojne.

00:22:35.279 --> 00:22:37.653
Prekleto, Guerrero.

00:22:37.653 --> 00:22:41.864
Sovražim, ko moram
prekinjati to zabavo tukaj,

00:22:41.864 --> 00:22:47.519
ker je pravi spektakel opazovati
te, medtem ko si v akciji.

00:22:47.799 --> 00:22:50.482
Toda moje potrpljenje
me zapušča.

00:22:50.682 --> 00:22:53.364
Takoj mi izroči, kar želim

00:22:53.960 --> 00:22:59.410
